==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bungler
<hw>Bun"gler</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A clumsy, awkward
workman; one who bungles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If to be a dunce or a <qex>bungler</qex> in any profession be
shameful, how much more ignominious and infamous to a scholar to be
such!</q> <rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>bunglesome</ent>⟦br⟧
